<div class="title">New Respect for the Pill</div>
<div class="substance">Amphetamines (Adderall)</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=JunkieJohn&Exact=1">JunkieJohn</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; JunkieJohn. "New Respect for the Pill: An Experience with Amphetamines (Adderall) (exp19839)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Aug 29, 2007. erowid.org/exp/19839</div>

<br/>



